hcamera
-------

Trivial EXIF image file tool.

To generate metadata files for MP4 videos type:

~~~~
exiftool -globalTimeShift +11:00 -S -w meta *.mp4
~~~~

To generate preview image for MP4 video type:

~~~~
avconv -i x.mp4 -f image2 -vframes 1 p/x.jpg
~~~~

Indirectly requires libexif:

    sudo apt-get install libexif-dev

The exiftool command is at:

   sudo apt-get install libimage-exiftool-perl

rd, 2008-2019
